===============================================================================
	DEVELOPER NOTES
===============================================================================

CVS tagging synApps
-------------------

All of the following have the same synApps release tag:

<top>/config - The *_RELEASE files define which release of each support module
		correspond to a particular release of synApps.

<top>/util   -	Since these are not support modules, and will not be separately
<top>/xxx	released from synApps; they are tagged along with synApps.

===============================================================================
	DEVELOPER ISSUES
===============================================================================

- If a user wants to link iocCore, seq and stdLib into <ioc>Lib, he will get
multiple definition errors unless dbLoadRecords, dbLoadTemplate, etc. are
removed from his version of EPICS base.  Non-VxWorks users have no choice
but to create one load module.
